#: ../../models/version_history.rst:70 c1ffdf342b1540e299b62f7b91c1e596
msgid ""
"For a detailed explanation of the architecture components (four-stage "
"pipeline, AudioVAE, Local DiT), see :doc:`./architecture`."
msgstr "架构组件（四阶段流水线、AudioVAE、Local DiT）的详细说明见 :doc:`./architecture`。"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:75 1465028b631e482ebb18197fb90f52a6
msgid ""
"VoxCPM 2 is the latest major release — a 2B parameter model trained on 2.36 "
"million hours of multilingual data. It represents a significant leap in "
"capacity, quality, and controllability over the 1.x series."
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM 2 是目前最新的大版本：一个在 236 万小时多语言数据上训练的 2B 参数模型。相较于 1.x "
"系列，它在规模、质量与可控性上都有显著提升。"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:77 ../../models/version_history.rst:94
#: ../../models/version_history.rst:108 4788d32e86c3445babf4f220d8c8c2d6
#: ae72d061245a4eb7a9b755de45465927 b8867b4b7cd24e8a8e7d17dda84298bb
msgid "Key characteristics:"
msgstr "主要特点："

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:79 9a04bf7b14a64826865ea890d003a4d0
msgid "48kHz audio output via AudioVAE V2 (asymmetric 16kHz encode → 48kHz decode)"
msgstr "通过 AudioVAE V2 输出 48kHz 音频（非对称 16kHz 编码 → 48kHz 解码）"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:80 ab7461a2019f4289905ea2f2fb51c0a4
msgid "30-language multilingual support"
msgstr "支持 30 种语言的合成"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:81 cb8323d07006449a84315d4014393abb
msgid ""
"Voice Design: create a voice from natural-language description, no reference"
" audio needed"
msgstr "Voice Design：用自然语言描述创建声线，无需参考音频"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:82 2e41431006f34755b205969f24648898
msgid ""
"Style Control: control emotion, pace, and speaking style of a cloned voice "
"via text tags"
msgstr "Style Control：通过文本标签控制克隆声音的情绪、语速与说话风格"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:83 3d93c77f215044818eae5841019fb090
msgid ""
"Isolated reference channel for voice cloning (no matching transcript "
"required)"
msgstr "为声音克隆提供隔离式参考通道（无需配套转写文本）"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:84 dd517a36fabe4df9a20352b3b6250832
msgid ""
"Concat-Projection residual LM fusion and multi-token DiT conditioning for "
"richer expressiveness"
msgstr "Concat-Projection 式 Residual LM 融合，结合多 token DiT 条件输入，带来更强的表现力"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:85 658f3a777dfe435d90c015521f05dcd0
msgid "Built on a `MiniCPM-4 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM>`_ backbone"
msgstr "基于 `MiniCPM-4 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM>`_ 骨干"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:87 d6401da1f0644f6ebd5d02c048390bdb
msgid ""
"Use VoxCPM 2 for all new projects. It is the recommended default for "
"multilingual synthesis, voice cloning, voice design, and production "
"deployment."
msgstr "新项目建议优先使用 VoxCPM 2。它是多语言合成、声音克隆、Voice Design 与生产部署的默认推荐版本。"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:92 7e16bf00ab6341a982bed53e8eaf05a3
msgid ""
"VoxCPM 1.5 is the final 1.x upgrade before VoxCPM 2. It improves audio "
"quality and efficiency while keeping the core context-aware generation and "
"zero-shot voice cloning workflow familiar to existing 1.x users."
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM 1.5 是 VoxCPM 2 之前 1.x 的最后一次升级。它在提升音质与效率的同时，保留原有 1.x "
"用户熟悉的上下文感知生成与零样本声音克隆流程。"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:96 42b5e23a1b8545f5bbfdb706d726c5b1
msgid "44.1kHz output"
msgstr "44.1kHz 输出"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:97 751dcfb1fc764efbac214af32efcf554
msgid "6.25Hz LM token rate"
msgstr "6.25Hz 的 LM token 速率"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:98 b31335f7ec4843d39e655aa0bb9e42d1
msgid "patch size increased from 2 to 4"
msgstr "patch 大小由 2 增至 4"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:99 794ee174b4094fea8c068fa12267d7b6
msgid "simpler migration path for existing VoxCPM 1.0 users"
msgstr "为既有 VoxCPM 1.0 用户提供更平滑的迁移路径"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:101 29c3e2cbea1f47a79ee006e66295c432
msgid ""
"Use VoxCPM 1.5 when you want a lighter Chinese/English checkpoint than "
"VoxCPM 2, while keeping stronger output quality than VoxCPM 1.0."
msgstr "若你需要比 VoxCPM 2 体量更小的中英 checkpoint，同时又希望输出质量优于 VoxCPM 1.0，可选用 VoxCPM 1.5。"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:106 06d15ae8fe7046ab8b16f8839f77280e
msgid ""
"VoxCPM 1.0 is the original tokenizer-free VoxCPM release. It remains useful "
"as the baseline reference point for the family and for older experiments "
"built around the original 0.5B checkpoint."
msgstr "VoxCPM 1.0 是初代无分词器 VoxCPM 发布版，仍可作为整个系列的基线参照，也适用于围绕原始 0.5B checkpoint 的早期实验。"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:110 64bba8413a0e417a8bdf2faf12c65ef9
msgid "600M parameter size"
msgstr "600M 参数量"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:111 b2c29c805af740ba92573bee4c941812
msgid "16kHz output"
msgstr "16kHz 输出"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:112 611c187a413945509031a44723b3d195
msgid "original VoxCPM architecture release"
msgstr "原始 VoxCPM 架构发布"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:113 c610c5cda36842aaa988031086012291
msgid "benchmark reference for early VoxCPM results"
msgstr "早期 VoxCPM 结果的基准参照"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:115 117d5d9608a54104a1f4dbdfc9c48781
msgid ""
"Use VoxCPM 1.0 when you need the smallest historical checkpoint or want to "
"compare against the original baseline behavior."
msgstr "若你需要体积最小的历史 checkpoint，或要与原始基线行为对比，可使用 VoxCPM 1.0。"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:118 e36b69cbbaf64043945f342c1a8c3cf9
msgid "Migration Guidance"
msgstr "迁移建议"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:120 34470b40afe2450d8a95658d6e457126
msgid "**New projects** should start with VoxCPM 2."
msgstr "**新项目** 请从 VoxCPM 2 开始。"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:121 26f0796a550f4ef1b49979a91a111904
msgid ""
"**Existing VoxCPM 1.0 users** should generally move to VoxCPM 1.5 first if "
"they need a lower-risk 1.x upgrade path."
msgstr "**既有 VoxCPM 1.0 用户** 若希望走风险更低的 1.x 升级路径，一般应先迁到 VoxCPM 1.5。"

#: ../../models/version_history.rst:122 581421a14ba44b1da6a9186de90fe620
msgid ""
"If you need multilingual synthesis, Voice Design, Style Control, or 48kHz "
"output, move directly to VoxCPM 2."
msgstr "若你需要多语种合成、Voice Design、Style Control 或 48kHz 输出，请直接升级到 VoxCPM 2。"

